Class AddPartForm

java.lang.Object
controller.AddPartForm
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class AddPartForm extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Author:
Huy G To The AddProductForm class is where users add a new part to the inventory. it allows a user to select whether the part be inhouse or outsourced, and has all the parameters of each corresponding option layed out on the textfields. saves on pressing the save button.
